Text: For a cheap movie, it's not that bad. Best to watch with friends so you can rip the hell out of it. But, it's still worth watching.. and it's really quite funny at times (on purpose.. I'm fairly sure it was.. I hope it was).
Actually, this movie is pretty good. Not on the level of the first Starship Troopers but good nonetheless.
extraordinary quality for an xvid rip - A/V - 10/10
